name: Kukaku Shiba | Bleach
description:
Submit your request here

v1.0

Weight: 1.0

Trigger + Appearance: shiba kukaku, (amputee, prosthetic arm:1.2), large breasts

Default Outfit: japanese clothes, bandages, cleavage

Add black hair if necessary.

The results of your generations are dependent on the additional LoRAs, weights, and models you use, so it may not work or come out as consistent as my sample images. Other reasons may include me using xformers, token merging, and a modified DPM++ 2M Karras sampler. You'll also notice that my prompt includes <lyco:. Note that all my LoRA files are located within my LyCORIS folder. If the model is labeled as a LoRA, it's a simple LoRA. If it's specified as a LyCORIS, it's a LoHa.

v0.1

Weight: 1.0

Trigger + Appearance: shiba kuukaku, (prosthesis, prosthetic arm:1.2), bandages, large breasts

Default Outfit: red dress, cleavage

The amputee prompt might work, it might not, same could be said for her prosthetic arm.

This is the first LoRA I trained on my laptop, this time using Lykon's AnyLoRA checkpoint as a training model. The result is mid, but I'm not disappointed. I realized that I had messed up on one of the settings after checking its metadata, but it's okay because it's all part of the fun experience that is baking a model for ~6 hours. I'll be learning from this to train another character tomorrow.
